tic function is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/64374/', '[1] "Product Information. ReVia (naltrexone)." DuPont Pharmaceuticals, Wilmington, DE.', 'Carisoprodol, Orphenadrine, Baclofen, Cyclobenzaprine, Methocarbamol, Chlormezanone', 'Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone, Celecoxib, Nalmefene, Nicotine, Acamprosate, Dexfenfluramine, Ephedrine, Phentermine, Orlistat, Lorcaserin, More', 1767369485);
